    <para styleclass="Heading3_atocs_"><anchor id="AssymetricalMotion" styleclass="Heading3_atocs_"><keywords><keyword translate="true">Segment-Range and Asymmetric Motion</keyword></keywords></anchor><text styleclass="Heading3_atocs_" translate="true">Asymmetric Motion</text></para>
    <para styleclass="Body Text"><table styleclass="Default" rowcount="3" colcount="1">
      <tr style="vertical-align:top">
        <td>
          <para styleclass="VariableName"><text styleclass="Body Text HowTo" translate="true">Use an </text><text styleclass="VariableName" translate="true">Asymmetric</text><text styleclass="Body Text HowTo" translate="true">&#32;</text><text styleclass="VariableName" translate="true">Modified-Sinusoid</text><text styleclass="Body Text" translate="true"> to </text><text styleclass="Body Text HowTo" translate="true">accelerate rapidly and decelerate more gradually, or </text><text styleclass="VariableName-IT" style="font-style:normal;" translate="true">vice versa</text><text styleclass="Body Text HowTo" translate="true">.</text></para>
          <para styleclass="VariableName"><text styleclass="Body Text HowTo" translate="true">You split one </text><text styleclass="VariableName" translate="true">Symmetric Modified-Sinusoid</text><text styleclass="Body Text HowTo" translate="true"> segment into two segments, and then use the </text><text styleclass="ParameterHeader" style="font-family:Arial; font-size:10pt; font-weight:normal; font-style:normal; text-decoration:none; text-transform:none; vertical-align:baseline; color:#000000; background-color:transparent; letter-spacing:normal; letter-scaling:100%;" translate="true">Segment-Range</text><text styleclass="Body Text HowTo" translate="true"> parameters to change the phase of the </text><link displaytype="text" defaultstyle="true" type="topiclink" href="MT-Cross-Over" styleclass="Body Text HowTo" style="font-style:normal;" translate="true">crossover</link><text styleclass="Body Text HowTo" translate="true"> to design the </text><text styleclass="VariableName" translate="true">Asymmetric</text><text styleclass="Body Text HowTo" translate="true">&#32;</text><text styleclass="VariableName" translate="true">Modified-Sinusoid</text><text styleclass="Body Text HowTo" translate="true">. </text></para>
          <para styleclass="Normal"><line style="height:1px; color:#993300;" /></para>
          <para styleclass="VariableName"><text styleclass="Body Text HowTo" translate="true">In the image below, we compare an </text><text styleclass="VariableName" translate="true">Asymmetric Modified Sinusoid</text><text styleclass="Body Text HowTo" translate="true"> (0 - 18</text><text styleclass="Body Table" translate="true">0</text><text styleclass="Body Text HowTo" translate="true">º) with a </text><text styleclass="VariableName" translate="true">Symmetric Modified Sinusoid</text><text styleclass="Body Text HowTo" translate="true"> (180 - 36</text><text styleclass="Body Table" translate="true">0</text><text styleclass="Body Text HowTo" translate="true">º) motion-law. </text></para>
          <para styleclass="VariableName"><text styleclass="Body Text HowTo" translate="true">The </text><link displaytype="text" defaultstyle="true" type="topiclink" href="MT-Cross-Over" styleclass="Body Text HowTo" style="font-style:normal;" translate="true">crossover</link><text styleclass="Body Text HowTo" translate="true"> of the </text><text styleclass="VariableName" translate="true">Asymmetric Modified-Sinusoid</text><text styleclass="Body Text HowTo" translate="true"> is at 60º, and the </text><link displaytype="text" defaultstyle="true" type="topiclink" href="MT-Cross-Over" styleclass="Body Text HowTo" style="font-style:normal;" translate="true">crossover</link><text styleclass="Body Text HowTo" translate="true"> of the </text><text styleclass="VariableName" translate="true">Symmetric Modified-Sinusoid</text><text styleclass="Body Text HowTo" translate="true"> is at 270º.</text></para>
        </td>
      </tr>
      <tr style="vertical-align:top">
        <td>
          <para styleclass="Normal"><image src="MT-AYMMETRIC-MOD-SINE.ipp" imagestyleclass="Default" scale="-99.90%" styleclass="Image Caption" figurelistinclude="0"><caption translate="true"><![CDATA[Asymmetric Mod-Sine   |   Symmetric Mod-Sine]]></caption></image></para>
        </td>
      </tr>
      <tr style="vertical-align:top">
        <td>
          <para styleclass="VariableName"><text styleclass="VariableName" translate="true">Asymmetrical Mod-Sine Segments : </text></para>
          <para styleclass="Heading4 Toggle_atocs_2"><equation styleclass="Heading4 Toggle_atocs_2" font-size="28" color="#000000" translate="true"><![CDATA[X-axis \ : 0 - 180\degree]]></equation></para>
          <para styleclass="Heading4 Toggle_atocs_2"><equation styleclass="Heading4 Toggle_atocs_2" font-size="28" color="#000000" translate="true"><![CDATA[Crossover\  at \ 60\degree]]></equation></para>
          <para styleclass="Heading4 Toggle_atocs_2"><equation styleclass="Heading4 Toggle_atocs_2" font-size="28" color="#000000" translate="true"><![CDATA[\therefore \ \lambda = \lfrac{60}{180} =  \lfrac{1}{3} ]]></equation></para>
          <para styleclass="Interface2"><text styleclass="Interface2" translate="true">Segment 1</text></para>
          <para styleclass="Body Text HowTo"><text styleclass="VariableName-indent" translate="true">Machine angle : </text><equation styleclass="VariableName;vertical-align:middle" style="font-family:Arial; font-size:10pt; font-weight:normal; font-style:normal; text-decoration:none; text-transform:none; vertical-align:baseline; color:#000000; background-color:transparent; letter-spacing:normal; letter-scaling:100%;" font-size="28" translate="true"><![CDATA[X-axis \ : 0 - 60\degree]]></equation><text styleclass="Body Text HowTo" translate="true">&#32;</text><text styleclass="VariableName" translate="true">( </text><equation styleclass="Body Text HowTo;vertical-align:text-bottom" style="font-family:Arial; font-size:10pt; font-weight:normal; font-style:normal; text-decoration:none; text-transform:none; vertical-align:baseline; color:#000000; background-color:transparent; letter-spacing:normal; letter-scaling:100%;vertical-align:text-bottom" font-size="28" translate="true"><![CDATA[\lfrac{1}{3}]]></equation><text styleclass="Body Text HowTo" translate="true"> of total Asymmetric motion-law</text><text styleclass="VariableName" translate="true"> )</text></para>
          <para styleclass="Body Text HowTo"><text styleclass="VariableName-indent" translate="true">Displacement : &#160;</text><equation styleclass="VariableName;vertical-align:middle" style="font-family:Arial; font-size:10pt; font-weight:normal; font-style:normal; text-decoration:none; text-transform:none; vertical-align:baseline; color:#000000; background-color:transparent; letter-spacing:normal; letter-scaling:100%;" font-size="28" translate="true"><![CDATA[Y-axis \ : 0 - 30mm]]></equation><text styleclass="Body Text HowTo" translate="true">&#32;</text><text styleclass="VariableName" translate="true">( </text><equation styleclass="Body Text HowTo;vertical-align:text-bottom" style="font-family:Arial; font-size:10pt; font-weight:normal; font-style:normal; text-decoration:none; text-transform:none; vertical-align:baseline; color:#000000; background-color:transparent; letter-spacing:normal; letter-scaling:100%;vertical-align:text-bottom" font-size="28" translate="true"><![CDATA[\lfrac{1}{3}]]></equation><text styleclass="Body Text HowTo" translate="true"> of total Asymmetric Displacement</text><text styleclass="VariableName" translate="true"> )</text></para>
          <para styleclass="Body Text HowTo"><text styleclass="Parameter" translate="true">Start-Range = 0</text><text styleclass="Parameter-Header" style="font-family:Arial; font-size:10pt; font-weight:normal; font-style:normal; text-decoration:none; text-transform:none; vertical-align:baseline; color:#000000; background-color:transparent; letter-spacing:normal; letter-scaling:100%;" translate="true"> ; </text><text styleclass="Parameter" translate="true">End Range = 0.5</text></para>
          <para styleclass="Interface2"><text styleclass="Interface2" translate="true">Segment 2</text></para>
          <para styleclass="Body Text HowTo"><text styleclass="VariableName-indent" translate="true">Machine angle : </text><equation styleclass="VariableName" font-size="28" translate="true"><![CDATA[X-axis \ : 60 - 180\degree]]></equation><text styleclass="VariableName" translate="true"> ( </text><equation styleclass="Body Text HowTo;vertical-align:text-bottom" style="font-family:Arial; font-size:10pt; font-weight:normal; font-style:normal; text-decoration:none; text-transform:none; vertical-align:baseline; color:#000000; background-color:transparent; letter-spacing:normal; letter-scaling:100%;vertical-align:text-bottom" font-size="28" translate="true"><![CDATA[\lfrac{2}{3}]]></equation><text styleclass="Body Text HowTo" translate="true"> of total Asymmetric motion-law</text><text styleclass="VariableName" translate="true"> )</text></para>
          <para styleclass="Body Text HowTo"><text styleclass="VariableName-indent" translate="true">Displacement : &#160;</text><equation styleclass="VariableName" font-size="28" translate="true"><![CDATA[Y-axis \ : 30 - 90mm ]]></equation><text styleclass="VariableName" translate="true"> ( </text><equation styleclass="Body Text HowTo;vertical-align:text-bottom" style="font-family:Arial; font-size:10pt; font-weight:normal; font-style:normal; text-decoration:none; text-transform:none; vertical-align:baseline; color:#000000; background-color:transparent; letter-spacing:normal; letter-scaling:100%;vertical-align:text-bottom" font-size="28" translate="true"><![CDATA[\lfrac{2}{3}]]></equation><text styleclass="Body Text HowTo" translate="true"> of total Asymmetric Displacement</text><text styleclass="VariableName" translate="true"> )</text></para>
          <para styleclass="Body Text HowTo"><text styleclass="Parameter" translate="true">Start-Range = 0.5</text><text styleclass="Parameter-Header" style="font-family:Arial; font-size:10pt; font-weight:normal; font-style:normal; text-decoration:none; text-transform:none; vertical-align:baseline; color:#000000; background-color:transparent; letter-spacing:normal; letter-scaling:100%;" translate="true">&#32;</text><text styleclass="Body Text" translate="true">;</text><text styleclass="Parameter-Header" style="font-family:Arial; font-size:10pt; font-weight:normal; font-style:normal; text-decoration:none; text-transform:none; vertical-align:baseline; color:#000000; background-color:transparent; letter-spacing:normal; letter-scaling:100%;" translate="true">&#32;</text><text styleclass="Parameter" translate="true">End Range = 1.0</text></para>
          <para styleclass="Normal"><line style="height:1px; color:#993300;" /></para>
          <para styleclass="VariableName"><text styleclass="VariableName" translate="true">Characteristics Values: Asymmetric and Symmetric Compared.</text></para>
          <para styleclass="Body Text HowTo"><table styleclass="Block" rowcount="3" colcount="2">
            <tr style="vertical-align:middle">
              <td style="width:203px;">
                <para styleclass="Body Text"><text styleclass="Body Text" translate="true">Velocity Coefficient : </text></para>
              </td>
              <td>
                <para styleclass="Popup Box"><equation styleclass="Body Text HowTo" font-size="28" translate="true"><![CDATA[Cv_{asym}=Cv_{sym}]]></equation></para>
              </td>
            </tr>
            <tr style="vertical-align:middle">
              <td style="width:203px;">
                <para styleclass="Body Text"><text styleclass="Body Text" translate="true">Acceleration Coefficient :</text></para>
              </td>
              <td>
                <para styleclass="Popup Box"><equation styleclass="Body Text HowTo" font-size="28" translate="true"><![CDATA[Ca_{asym}=\lfrac{Ca_{sym}}{2\lambda}]]></equation></para>
              </td>
            </tr>
            <tr style="vertical-align:middle">
              <td style="width:203px;">
                <para styleclass="Body Text"><text styleclass="Body Text" translate="true">Deceleration Coefficient : </text></para>
              </td>
              <td>
                <para styleclass="Popup Box"><equation styleclass="Body Text HowTo" font-size="28" translate="true"><![CDATA[Ca_{asym} = \lfrac{Ca_{sym}}{2\left( 1-\lambda \right)}]]></equation></para>
              </td>
            </tr>
          </table></para>
        </td>
      </tr>
    </table></para>
